title: Remove Duplicates from Array
description: In this problem, you are given a sorted array of integers. Your task is to identify and process the unique elements in the array. Since the array is sorted, duplicates will appear consecutively. You need to print strictly the unique elements from the input array.
input_format: A single line containing space-separated integers (sorted).
output_format: Output the unique elements of the array in a single line, separated by spaces.
